CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1953, pg. 27, reads: "Novice Swim Meet - The City Recreation Department held its annual novice swimming meet last Thursday at Moore Pool in Brookline... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Swimmers performing backstroke, with man standing near edge of pool on left, for City Recreation Department swim meet, at Moore Pool, Brookline
